description: Compatible with most iPods, the F8Z126 AV Dock and Charger lets you view your video content on your TV and listen to music through your home audio system. It comes with adapter inserts for iPod nano 1st and 2nd generation and iPod 5th generation (video). This convenient and easy-to-use system includes everything you need to sync, charge, and play your iPod, and is backed by a three-year warranty.What's in the BoxPower dock with AV out, 6-foot USB-to-mini-USB cable, dock-adapter inserts for iPod nano 1st and 2nd generation and iPod 5th generation (video) models, AC power adapter, and user's manual.
title: Belkin F8Z126 Power Dock AV for iPod
